title: It would be ‘lunacy,’ ‘horrible for this country’ if big states voted before Iowa, NH
text: FORT DODGE, Iowa — Sen. Ted Cruz (R-Tex.) opened a packed swing through early voting Iowa on Monday by blasting leaders in his own party for contemplating changes to the presidential primary calendar, calling it “lunacy” and a “terrible idea.” Reince Priebus, the chairman of the Republican National Committee, recently suggested the party could tweak […] ...
